name: vp2Line

vp2Line
vp2InspectFunction
func:
let toggle = context.get("toggle") || 0;
let chSelection = flow.get("vp2chSelection") || 0;
let unit = {};

if(!toggle) /* First time */
{
    flow.set("vpInspect", true);
    unit = 
    {
        groups: 
        { 
            show: [
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp1",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp3",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp4",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp5"
            ],
            hide: 
            [
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Battery",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ODR",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Temperature",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_x",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_y",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_z",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_x",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_y",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_z",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_x",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_y",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_z",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ODR2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Temperature2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_x2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_y2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_z2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_x2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_y2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_z2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_x2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_y2",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_z2"
            ],
            disable: 
            [
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2SelectMAC",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Download",
                "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2switch"
            ]
        } 
    }
    toggle++;
}
else /* Second time */
{
    flow.set("vpInspect", false);
    if(chSelection == false)
    {
        unit = 
        {
            groups: 
            { 
                hide: 
                [
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp1",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp3",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp4",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp5",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ODR2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Temperature2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_x2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_y2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_z2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_x2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_y2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_z2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_x2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_y2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_z2"
                ],
                show: [
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Battery",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ODR",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Temperature",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_x",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_y",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_z",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_x",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_y",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_z",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_x",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_y",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_z"
                ],
                enable : 
                [
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2SelectMAC",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Download",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2switch"
                ]
            } 
        }
    }
    if(chSelection == true) 
    {
        unit =
        {
            groups:
            {
                hide:
                [
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp1",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp3",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp4",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Insp5",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ODR",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Temperature",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_x",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_y",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_z",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_x",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_y",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_z",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_x",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_y",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_z"
                ],
                show: 
                [
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Battery",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ODR2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Temperature2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_x2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_y2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2ACCGroup_z2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_x2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_y2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2VelDisplGroup_z2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_x2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_y2",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2OneTwoThreeGroup_z2"
                ],
                enable:
                [
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2SelectMAC",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2Download",
                    "ncd-2ch-vibration:vp2switch"
                ]
            }
        }
    }
    toggle = 0;
}
context.set("toggle", toggle);
msg.payload = unit;
return msg;
